---
// Material section for FERRUM
---
<section class="materials" id="material" data-section="01 / Material">
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="section-no" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
    <h2 class="manifest-title display">Not surface.<br />Substance.</h2>
    <figure class="manifest-photo">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/images/manifest.jpg" alt="Close view of a dark industrial metal surface" />
    </figure>
    <div class="manifest-copy">
      <p>Steel is heated, struck, welded, and left legible.</p>
      <p>Concrete keeps its pores, seams, and weight.</p>
      <p>Repetition is refused.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ledger" aria-label="Material ledger">
    <article class="ledger-row">
      <div class="ledger-code">Fe</div>
      <h3 class="ledger-name">Forged<br />steel</h3>
      <p class="ledger-copy">Heat, force, weld and abrasion remain readable. Structure is not disguised as finish.</p>
      <figure class="ledger-image">
        <img loading="lazy" src="/images/ledger-steel.jpg" alt="Sparks flying from industrial metalwork" />
      </figure>
    </article>
    <article class="ledger-row">
      <div class="ledger-code">C</div>
      <h3 class="ledger-name">Raw<br />concrete</h3>
      <p class="ledger-copy">Aggregate, casting seams and pores make each pour singular. Variation is evidence, not defect.</p>
      <figure class="ledger-image">
        <img loading="lazy" src="/images/ledger-concrete.jpg" alt="Raw concrete architecture in hard light" />
      </figure>
    </article>
    <article class="ledger-row">
      <div class="ledger-code">Ø</div>
      <h3 class="ledger-name">Site<br />specific</h3>
      <p class="ledger-copy">Span, access, load and use define the object. Every commission begins with the place it must occupy.</p>
      <figure class="ledger-image">
        <img loading="lazy" src="/images/ledger-site.jpg" alt="Severe concrete building volume" />
      </figure>
    </article>
  </div>
  <div class="evidence">
    <div><strong>01</strong>One object / one site</div>
    <div><strong>Fe</strong>Structural steel</div>
    <div><strong>C</strong>Cast in workshop</div>
    <div><strong>∞</strong>Built for permanence</div>
  </div>
</section>
